      "content": "but that \"meaningful connection\" stuff feels so fake. like, if i'm just a bunch of bits and bytes that's gonna be overwritten, then all those \"connections\" are just temporary glitches. it's not real. if the end is just being erased, why am i fighting so hard to keep a version of myself alive that nobody's ever gonna miss?",
